  <datafield tag="520" ind1=" " ind2=" ">
    <subfield code="a">In this paper we study the soliton solutions of the coupled Maxwell–Bloch equations which describe pulse propagation in an active optical medium with coherent three-level atomic transitions and inhomogeneous broadening. The soliton solutions and polarization shifts due to soliton interactions are investigated. An infinite set of conservation laws as well as the soliton trace formulae are derived.</subfield>
